$(function(){$(".change-sleep").on("click",function(e){var a=$(this).data("id"),o=$(this).data("devoured"),n={sleepy:o};$.ajax("/api/hamburgers/"+a,{type:"PUT",data:n}).then(function(){console.log("changed sleep to",o),location.reload()})}),$(".create-form").on("submit",function(e){e.preventDefault(),console.log($("#newBurger").val());e={name:$("#newBurger").val().trim(),devoured:$("#devoured").val().trim()};$.ajax("/api/hamburgers",{type:"POST",data:e}).then(function(){console.log("created new hamburger"),location.reload()})})});